The paper discusses the limitations of current question answering systems and proposes a new approach based on natural language understanding and reasoning in a knowledge-based environment. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and cybernetics (cs.CY).
